Lord Nagafen Sunday March 30th. 1pm est<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Who: 6ish groups of adventurers levels 48-52*<br>
What: Naggy Smackdown<br>
Where: In Nagafen’s Lair, but meet at Druid Rings in Lavastorm First<br>
When: Sunday March 30th at 1:00pm Eastern Time (please note this is 10:00am pacific time)<br>
Why: For fun.<br>
Bring: Your resist gear, 2 peridots and one pearl, and your fun attitude.<br>
*Note: Clerics level 39-52 with Complete Heal are welcome to come along as are Bards of level 45-52.  High level buffers are encouraged to contact me about prebuffing the raid in exchange for a random roll on a naggy item.<br>
<br>
Loot: to be rolled /random 1000. Once you win something you stop rolling. Duplicates of any drop are reserved. Uber buffers (60+)will receive a /random 1000 roll on the naggy drop of their choice. Please note that some items though usable by a class are not rollable on by that class in order to try to entice more varied classes to attend the raid.<br>
Torn, Burnt Book PAL (only no drop loot off naggy) (epic piece) (duplicates of this item are NOT reserved)<br>
Red Dragon Scale BRD, WAR (epic piece)<br>
Cloak of Flames PAL, WAR, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG, BST, MNK<br>
Treasure Hunter’s Satchel NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC, MNK, DRU, CLR, SHM<br>
Selo's Drums of the March BRD<br>
Blight, Hammer of the Scourge SHM<br>
Heirophant’s Crook DRU<br>
Gauntlets of fiery might PAL, WAR, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG, BST, MNK<br>
Orb of Tishan NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC<br>
Bladestopper CLR<br>
Gold plated Koshigatana WAR, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG, NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC<br>
Prayers Of Life NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC, DRU, CLR, SHM<br>
Red Dragon Tooth NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC, DRU, CLR, SHM<br>
Rokyl’s Channeling Crystal Reserved<br>
Polished Mithril Mask (No Drop) Improved Damage 2. NEC, MAG, WIZ, ENC, CLR<br>
Dormant Crystal Sphere (No Drop) DRU, CLR (Worship Karana) Item is for a quest<br>
Razing Sword of Skarlon (No Drop) PAL, WAR, SHD<br>
Mithril Vambraces PAL, WAR, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG (please only roll on this if it is an upgrade for you)<br>
Mithril Greaves PAL, WAR, RNG, SHD, BRD, ROG (please only roll on this if it is an upgrade for you)<br>
Crown of King Tranix CLR, ENC<br>
Polished Mithril Torque (No Drop) WAR PAL RNG SHD MNK BRD ROG BST<br>
Other vendor trash rolled on by appropriate classes or sold to defray raid expenses at raid leader’s discretion.<br>
<br>
==================================<br>
<br>
Groups will be formed at the Druid Rings In Lavastorm at 1:00PM EST. We will then junk buff, get an uber buff or two, then head in to slay giants and then Lord Nagafen himself. We should be out of there by 3:00pm if people are on time.<br>
<br>
Please send me an email in advance to secure a spot for your character and i will send you a confirmation invite in return and more info the week of the raid.<br>
